General.Name: Legend Mining Ltd
General.Description: Legend Mining Limited engages in the exploration of nickel and copper deposits in Australia. The company also explores for cobalt, zinc, silver, and gold deposits. It holds interests in the Rockford project consisting of 14 granted exploration licenses that cover a total area of 2,993 square kilometers located in the Fraser Range district of Western Australia. Legend Mining Limited was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
